    <h3><a id="adding">Adding Bootstrap</a></h3>
      To add Bootstrap to your project/website you go to the <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/getting-started/">Bootstrap</a> site
      and copy the "CDN code" to put it in the 'head' part of your web app.
  </pre>

